{"tid":2432341,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"錄到愛妻嬌吟「不要再弄內褲都濕了」 法官判決：不用賠","createTime":"2021-03-04T09:03:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T13:47:35.000Z","uid":1886,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b3446d3464bf759af3926cbd30a02533f82d1afe","tid":2432341,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T09:03:01.000Z","msg":"邱姓新娘秘書的老公陳男見妻子的愛車太久沒洗，自告奮勇捲袖洗車，赫然發現行車紀錄器內有疑似妻子偷吃小王的呻吟聲，妻子竟嬌嗔：「下次請你戴套，不准弄到裡面，也不能弄到我的嘴巴裡面！」東窗事發後邱女只求離婚，陳男氣她背叛婚姻卻毫無悔意，憤而求償100萬元，然而法官雖認定錄音檔有證據力，卻因已超過2年的請求權時效而愛莫能助，僅能判人夫敗訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/society/breakingnews/3455331\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fbreakingnews%2F3455331&d=Xhragic3nybqeCAZBODyv9agwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=2a2b272f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fbreakingnews%2F3455331&h=6232c0b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/society/breakingnews/3455331</a>"},{"pid":"2875b852fe238345680547a16424e13745f1274d","tid":2432341,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T09:03:31.000Z","msg":"陳男指控，與邱女結婚8年，育有2子，夫妻生活本來幸福美滿，次子出生後，妻子表示希望外出從事新娘秘書工作，要求買車作交通工具，半年後，妻子開始藉詞工作需要就開車外出，他關心之餘詢問去向，妻子即怒目以對，埋怨他過問太多。"},{"pid":"ce014dd05548ce50baedc9b5f8727f98ea3e27bd","tid":2432341,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T09:03:58.000Z","msg":"某日他見妻子忙於工作而沒有時間清洗愛車，幫太太洗車之際，見車上有行車紀錄器，一時好奇而播放，竟是妻子與小王的呻吟聲及曖昧對話，邱女：「不要再弄她，你看整個褲子都濕了、内褲都濕了，你自己摸！」小王：「我摸！我摸！」邱女：「下次請你戴套，不准給我這樣子，弄到我的裡面，也不能弄到我的嘴巴裡面！」"},{"pid":"5b70a07ef2423787d8c864a4d5354f98ca3dda03","tid":2432341,"uid":34553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T09:04:13.000Z","msg":"以為係天真嬌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dc221629238ed3b1cbfd07af240512667666aa8","tid":2432341,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T09:04:18.000Z","msg":"妻子見偷吃小王一事已經東窗事發，亦不再隱瞞，並表示既然已經這樣，她什麼都可以不要，只要能離婚就好，兩人在2018年10月離婚。<br />\n<br />\n陳男不甘原本美滿婚姻一夕之間全盤皆沒，妻子對婚姻家庭的背叛，至今仍毫無悔意，他每每思及遭枕邊人無情背叛，即痛徹心扉，輾轉難眠，數度瀕臨崩潰，因此向邱女求償100萬元，聊以慰藉。<br />\n<br />\n法官調查，陳男在2018年8月即已知悉妻子偷吃小王，卻遲至去年9月30 日才提起本案訴訟，侵權行為損害賠償請求權顯已超過2年時效而消滅。儘管法官認定本案錄音檔有證據力，卻只能判人夫敗訴，全案駁回。"},{"pid":"6edd33cfd0cd3cfead256d938cbd61278229d470","tid":2432341,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T09:04:31.000Z","msg":"新竹+1"},{"pid":"a6e5d6555ad1f7aad5f1bec8cdb1bad076cd78d9","tid":2432341,"uid":10014,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T09:06:25.000Z","msg":"其實呢啲真係悲哀<br />\n對女人好真係無好下場"},{"pid":"f88376912d65687a009b69d365d99ea18e668d7d","tid":2432341,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T09:07:01.000Z","msg":"所以話"},{"pid":"b4c8a26e4845c5956718d4d51fe9feb8cefce953","tid":2432341,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T09:07:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c03a93bfc925842214d4845f66ce42d7b5430b2a","tid":2432341,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6edd33cfd0cd3cfead256d938cbd61278229d470","tid":2432341,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T09:04:31.000Z","msg":"新竹+1"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T09:07:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d9f966b4e8e6a7a1c2563690d3187082c7c5fd2","tid":2432341,"uid":51057,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T09:10:29.000Z","msg":"等2年先走去告<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0dd0cde5977f6f2b44929f818c24b4a26aa2af7","tid":24